01:31:09,740 --> 01:31:10,290
Ke sumber air panas.

1439
01:31:10,290 --> 01:31:11,290
Oke!

1440
01:31:15,140 --> 01:31:16,958
Tenang!

1441
01:31:18,832 --> 01:31:19,993
Jangan takut!

1442
