1445
01:31:34,589 --> 01:31:35,713
Kau memelukku terlalu erat.

1446
01:31:35,714 --> 01:31:37,179
Terlalu ketat, Ke Er.

1447
01:31:38,988 --> 01:31:40,546
Jangan lepaskan!

1448
01:31:40,646 --> 01:31:42,020
Jadi ternyata di dunia
ini, selain garis lurus.

1449
01:31:42,021 --> 01:31:45,496
